"and from provisional data for years 2025 and later, as compiled from data provided by the 57 vital statistics jurisdictions"
"through the Vital Statistics Cooperative Program. Accessed at http://wonder.cdc.gov/mcd-icd10-provisional.html on Apr 13, 2026"
"7:22:54 PM"
